made into a limited TV series.

00:37:55.400 --> 00:37:56.700
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Congratulations.

00:37:56.700 --> 00:37:58.040
&gt;&gt; Dan Chaon: Yeah, I'm not
sure how that's going to look

00:37:58.040 --> 00:38:01.210
